entries.title: Trump unveils new education policy loaded with culture war proposals
entries.description: The proposal reflects the degree to which Republicans want the next election to be waged around classrooms as much as boardrooms.

entries.title: Adams outlines ‘Working People’s Agenda’ in State of the City speech
DeSantis scrambles RNC race after praising Dhillon and urging ‘new blood’
entries.description: The Florida governor weighed in on the race just 24 hours before the RNC’s 168 voting members are set to elect their next chair on Friday.
